  "keyFeatures": [
    "OpenTelemetry-compatible semantic conventions for AI observability",
    "Multi-language support (Python, JavaScript, Java)",
    "30+ instrumentation libraries for popular AI frameworks",
    "Automatic tracing for LLMs, agents, tools, and retrievers",
    "Privacy controls and PII masking",
    "Token counting and cost tracking",
    "Context propagation for session and user tracking",
    "Comprehensive span kinds (LLM, Agent, Chain, Tool, Retriever, etc.)",
    "Support for multimodal content and tool calling"
